{"tid":848816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平涉貪】獄中教毒犯「語言藝術」助取中學證書 獲法官致謝","createTime":"2018-10-05T08:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T08:20:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d4beb204c77ba06aed60a4cfdef6cbd24e00ae8a","tid":848816,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181005/large/1538678732_0502.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181005%2Flarge%2F1538678732_0502.png&h=3a7b6e1d&s={SIZE}\" /> 《蘋果》製圖<br />\n<br />\n何志平的保釋申請雖然再次被拒，但法官Loletta Preska在聆訊中特別感謝何志平在獄中協助一名由她判刑的毒犯，以導師身份助他完成中學證書課程。翻查紀錄，何志平在獄中每周用8小時替該毒犯補習數學及語言藝術，並為他向法官寫求情信。<br />\n<br />\n法官Preska在聆訊期間，感謝何志平向她判刑的一名毒犯提供輔導及建議，何就在座位點頭回應。翻查紀錄，該名毒犯是37歲的Jonathan Weeks，他在2016年9月被捕，案件一直審理至今年9月，才被Preska判處罪成，並判監5年。期間他一直還柙在大都會懲教中心，與何志平成為囚友。<br />\n<br />\n根據Weeks的判刑陳述書，他在獄中進修相等於高中文憑的「普通教育發展證書（General Education Development &ldquo;GED&rdquo; certificate）」，並獲得本身在獄中擔當GED導師的何志平的協助。信中指何志平在過去幾個月，每星期有4個早晨、每次花兩小時協助Weeks學習數學及語言藝術（Language Arts）兩個科目，最終助自小就多次進出監獄的他成功取得證書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何志平並為Weeks撰寫求情信，陳述書節錄了求情信，何志平在當中指Weeks對學習及成功的積極性令他印象深刻，形容對方每一課都非常自律地參與，非常願意聆聽及學習，展現出熱誠及專注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181005/58757896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58757896&d=zvLao%2BSuoI6dBvlu%2B1mtdPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=3e0dc6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F58757896&h=4d6fca1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181005/58757896</a><br />\n<br />\n肥平係監獄生活得好開心咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f39abde7a7e0ba60a5d450a148b01212a542b05","tid":848816,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fe564195b4bed3e0bf667638e79ecbdb0427e6","tid":848816,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"難得難得， 身體力行將一帶一路帶到美國獄中"},{"pid":"803ab0cb80c4dc71d32239a04463fa950fab1b6a","tid":848816,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"183030132d3794c34b19def8d57a9d4609c36a27","tid":848816,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"喺美國傳揚中式語言藝術，發展勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好心美國佬醒少少放咗佢啦，遲啲成個監獄都係肥平門生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}